{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriétés</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload\"><code>onload</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend\"><code>onloadend</code></a></li><li><em><code>onloadstart</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propriété <strong><code>onloadstart</code></strong> du \"mixin\" <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> (<em>gestionnaire d'évènements</em>) représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'évènement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadstart (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché (quand la progression est commencée sur le chargement d'une ressource).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onloadstart <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> funcRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valeur","title":"Valeur","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>funcRef</code> est la fonction du gestionnaire à appeler lorsque l'évènement <code>loadstart</code> de la ressource est déclenché.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemples","title":"Exemples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contenu_html","title":"Contenu HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>myImage.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contenu_javascript","title":"Contenu JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 'loadstart' est lancé le premier, puis 'load', puis 'loadend'</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'load'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image loaded'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'loadstart'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image load started'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'loadend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image load finished'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spécifications","title":"Spécifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Spécification</th>\n      <th>Statut</th>\n      <th>Commentaire</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onloadstart\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'onloadstart' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Standard évolutif</span></td>\n      <td>Définition initiale.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntaxe","id":"syntaxe"},{"text":"Exemples","id":"exemples"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"}],"summary":"La propriété onloadstart du \"mixin\" GlobalEventHandlers est un event handler (gestionnaire d'évènements) représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'évènement loadstart (en-US) est déclenché (quand la progression est commencée sur le chargement d'une ressource).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onloadstart","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onloadstart/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadstart - Référence Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}